<subSubSection id="C3216579FFD9FFCECA99C194207F6AFA" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="8B8436F2FFD9FFCECA99C194207F6AFA" blockId="8.[151,1437,1405,1755]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">
This species is distributed from southern 
<collectingCountry id="F32C7662FFD9FFCEC869C1972395699D" box="[615,694,1442,1468]" name="France" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">France</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F32C7662FFD9FFCEC8CFC19423D6699A" box="[705,757,1441,1467]" name="Italy" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">Italy</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F32C7662FFD9FFCEC90FC19422A4699A" box="[769,903,1441,1467]" name="Switzerland" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">Switzerland</collectingCountry>
across southern,central and Eastern Europe all to northern 
<collectingCountry id="F32C7662FFD9FFCECB49C1F3205769C1" box="[327,372,1478,1504]" name="Iraq" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">Iraq</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="F32C7662FFD9FFCECBA6C1F0230869FE" box="[424,555,1477,1503]" name="Kazakhstan" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">Kazakhstan</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCEC836C1F0220569FE" author="Naumann, C. M. &amp; Tarmann, G. M. &amp; Tremewan, W. G." box="[568,806,1477,1503]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" refId="ref10290" refString="Naumann, C. M., Tarmann, G. M. &amp; Tremewan, W. G. (1999) The western Palaearctic Zygaenidae (Lepidoptera). Apollo, Stenstrup, 304 pp." type="book" year="1999">
Naumann 
<emphasis id="B94FEAE0FFD9FFCEC8A3C1F323C669FE" box="[685,741,1477,1503]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">et al.</emphasis>
1999
</bibRefCitation>
). Several historical records exist for this species in 
<collectingCountry id="F32C7662FFD9FFCECF52C1F021C16A22" name="Croatia" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">Croatia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCECAFEC1DC20566A25" author="Mann, J." box="[240,373,1513,1540]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="139 - 189" refId="ref9850" refString="Mann, J. (1857) Verzeichnis der im Jahre 1853 in der Gegend von Fiume gesammelten Schmetterlinge. Wiener entomologische Monatschrift, 1, 139 - 189." type="journal article" year="1857">Mann 1857</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCECB70C1DC23B86A22" author="Abafy-Aigner, L. &amp; Pavel, J. &amp; Uhryk, F." box="[382,667,1513,1539]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="1 - 82" refId="ref9194" refString="Abafy-Aigner, L., Pavel, J. &amp; Uhryk, F. (1896) Fauna Regni Hungariae. Ordo Lepidoptera. Regia Societas Scientiarum Naturalium Hungarica, 3, 1 - 82." type="journal article" year="1896">
Abafy-Aigner 
<emphasis id="B94FEAE0FFD9FFCEC82CC1DF23796A22" box="[546,602,1513,1539]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">et al.</emphasis>
1896
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCEC8A8C1DC220A6A22" author="Rebel, H." box="[678,809,1513,1539]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="97 - 377" refId="ref10440" refString="Rebel, H. (1904) Studien uber die Lepidopterenfauna der Balkanlander. II. Teil. Bosnien und Herzegowina. Annalen des Naturhistorischen Museums in Wien, 19, 97 - 377." type="journal article" year="1904">Rebel 1904</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCEC93DC1DC224D6A22" author="Rebel, H." box="[819,878,1513,1539]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="97 - 110" refId="ref10475" refString="Rebel, H. (1910) Lepidopteren aus dem Gebiete des Monte Maggiore in Istrien. XXI. Jahresbericht des Wiener entomologischen Vereines, 1910, 97 - 110." type="journal article" year="1910">1910</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCEC974C1DC25156A22" author="Schawerda, K." box="[890,1078,1513,1539]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="10 - 11" refId="ref10594" refString="Schawerda, K. (1920) Lepidopteren-Ausbeute aus der Gegend von Lovrana und Monte Maggiore. Zeitschrift des Osterreichischen Entomologischen Vereins, 5, 10 - 11 + 20 - 21 + 28 + 36 + 43." type="journal article" year="1920">Schawerda 1920</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCECE4FC1DC25F46A22" author="Stauder, H." box="[1089,1239,1513,1539]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="1 - 4" refId="ref10678" refString="Stauder, H. (1921) Die Zygaenidenarmut der adriatischen Inseln. Societas entomologica, 36, 1 - 4." type="journal article" year="1921">Stauder 1921</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCECEEDC1DC243D6A22" author="Stauder, H." box="[1251,1310,1513,1539]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="35 - 39" refId="ref10700" refString="Stauder, H. (1932) Die Schmetterlingsfauna der illyro-adriatischen Festland- und Inselzone [Faunula Illiyro-Adriatica]. Entomologischen Anzeiger 12, 35 - 39 + 53 - 54 + 71 - 72 + 92 + 131 - 132 + 150 - 152 + 200 + 233 - 234 + 256." type="journal article" year="1932">1932</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCECF27C1DF20226A09" author="Neustetter, H." pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="4 - 8" refId="ref10328" refString="Neustetter, H. (1956) Sammelreisen nach Dalmatien (Jugoslavien). Entomologisches Nachrichtenblatt, 3, 4 - 8." type="journal article" year="1956">Neustetter 1956</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCECB03C238209C6A06" author="Carnelutti, J." box="[269,447,1549,1575]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="185 - 223" refId="ref9288" refString="Carnelutti, J. (1994) Modernisiertes &quot; Verzeichnis der bei Knin gesammelten Schmetterlinge &quot; von Ivan Hafner. Natura Croatica, 3, 185 - 223." type="journal article" year="1994">Carnelutti 1994</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCECBC5C23823466A06" author="Habeler, H." box="[459,613,1549,1575]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" refId="ref9434" refString="Habeler, H. (2008) Die Schmetterlinge der Adria-Insel Krk. Eine okofaunistische Studie. Delta Druck, Verlag Heinz Peks, Graz, 221 pp." type="book" year="2008">Habeler 2008</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCEC87FC23A220C6A09" author="Sasic, M. &amp; Nahirnic, A. &amp; Tarmann, G. M." box="[625,815,1549,1578]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="233 - 248" refId="ref10538" refString="Sasic, M., Nahirnic, A. &amp; Tarmann, G. M. (2016) Zygaenidae (Lepidoptera) in the Lepidoptera collections of the Croatian Natu- ral History Museum. Natura Croatica, 25, 233 - 248. https: // doi. org / 10.20302 / NC. 2016.25.19" type="journal article" year="2016">
Å aÅ¡iÄ 
<emphasis id="B94FEAE0FFD9FFCEC8BDC23B23C86A06" box="[691,747,1549,1575]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">et al.</emphasis>
2016
</bibRefCitation>
). However, the last record of this species in 
<collectingCountry id="F32C7662FFD9FFCECF13C238244C6A06" box="[1309,1391,1549,1575]" name="Croatia" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">Croatia</collectingCountry>
has been in 1973 (
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCECB6DC206233E6A6D" author="Sasic, M. &amp; Nahirnic, A. &amp; Tarmann, G. M." box="[355,541,1585,1614]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" pagination="233 - 248" refId="ref10538" refString="Sasic, M., Nahirnic, A. &amp; Tarmann, G. M. (2016) Zygaenidae (Lepidoptera) in the Lepidoptera collections of the Croatian Natu- ral History Museum. Natura Croatica, 25, 233 - 248. https: // doi. org / 10.20302 / NC. 2016.25.19" type="journal article" year="2016">
Å aÅ¡iÄ 
<emphasis id="B94FEAE0FFD9FFCECBA8C20720F56A6A" box="[422,470,1585,1611]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">et al</emphasis>
. 2016
</bibRefCitation>
) so the records presented in this work are first records after 57 years. During this survey, the species has been recorded on three localities within two biogeographical regions (
<figureCitation id="13002A77FFD9FFCECEC1C26024306A4E" box="[1231,1299,1621,1647]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="15.[151,250,1827,1851]" captionTargetBox="[209,1379,224,1764]" captionTargetId="figure-15@15.[166,1422,181,1784]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 8. Distribution of Jordanita chloros in Croatia based on newly collected data and historical records." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4643405" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4643405/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
). According to 
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B03FFD9FFCECAECC24F20FD6AB2" author="Naumann, C. M. &amp; Tarmann, G. M. &amp; Tremewan, W. G." box="[226,478,1657,1684]" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" refId="ref10290" refString="Naumann, C. M., Tarmann, G. M. &amp; Tremewan, W. G. (1999) The western Palaearctic Zygaenidae (Lepidoptera). Apollo, Stenstrup, 304 pp." type="book" year="1999">
Naumann 
<emphasis id="B94FEAE0FFD9FFCECB5BC24F20AE6AB2" box="[341,397,1657,1683]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">et al.</emphasis>
(1999)
</bibRefCitation>
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D71FFD9FFCECBEBC24F23726AB2" authority="Efetov &amp; Tarmann, 1999" authorityName="Efetov &amp; Tarmann" authorityYear="1999" baseAuthorityName="Hubner" baseAuthorityYear="1813" box="[485,593,1657,1683]" class="Insecta" family="Zygaenidae" genus="Jordanita" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="69" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chloros">
<emphasis id="B94FEAE0FFD9FFCECBEBC24F23726AB2" box="[485,593,1657,1683]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">J. chloros</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
inhabits dry grassy slopes and steppe biotopes. While only three specimens were recorded during this survey, it seems that the habitat in 
<collectingCountry id="F32C7662FFD9FFCEC971C2A822F26A96" box="[895,977,1693,1719]" name="Croatia" pageId="8" pageNumber="69">Croatia</collectingCountry>
is also in accordance with the one from the literature.
</paragraph>
